OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,FThe capital's political landscape has
OL,8,Fchanged dramatically over the past 24
OL,9,Fhours.
OL,11,FTwo days ago 21 of 32 London boroughs
OL,12,Fwere run by Labour. There are now
OL,13,Fcurrently, just nine.
OL,15,FLabour has lost control of the London
OL,16,Fborough of Lambeth for the first time
OL,17,Fin 20 years, marking another major
OL,18,Fblow for the party in the capital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
