OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,FThe party won 26 of the 63 seats,
OL,8,Fwhile the Greens took 29 seats,
OL,9,Fbecoming the largest party but failing
OL,10,Fto secure overall control, while the
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats took eight seats.
OL,13,FIt is the latest in a series of heavy
OL,14,Flosses for Labour in the capital,
OL,15,Fwhile the Green Party won four London
OL,16,Felections and Reform took control of
OL,17,Fits first London council in Havering.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,FWhile the Greens did not secure a
OL,8,Ftotal victory, the party's Lambeth
OL,9,Fgroup leader Scott Ainslie, said
OL,10,FLabour losing control of Lambeth was
OL,11,Fstill a "historic" moment.
OL,13,F"Lambeth Greens are proud and honoured
OL,14,Fto have won the confidence of so many
OL,15,Fvoters across this borough," he said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
