CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,F"We will work every day to give them a
OL,8,Fvoice, push back austerity, and make
OL,9,Fthis borough the best place to live,
OL,10,Fwork and have fun. We will put their
OL,11,Fright to a decent affordable home, a
OL,12,Fliveable environment, and fulfilled
OL,13,Flife ahead of the interests of
OL,14,Fdevelopers and speculators.
OL,16,F"We will make this a council that
OL,17,Flistens and empowers. Thank you to
OL,18,Feveryone who voted, to all of our
OL,19,Fvolunteers, and to all of the council
OL,20,Fstaff who have worked so hard to
OL,21,Fdeliver the election."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,FLabour is still the biggest party on
OL,8,FCroydon Council, which remains under
OL,9,Fno overall control.
OL,11,FThe party won 30 seats, followed by
OL,12,Fthe Conservatives with 27.
OL,14,FMayor of London, Sir Sadiq Khan said:
OL,16,F"It's been a bitterly disappointing
OL,17,Fset of elections for Labour in London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,F"Great Labour councils are no longer
OL,8,FLabour councils, Great Labour
OL,9,Fcouncillors have lost their seats and
OL,10,Fit's incredibly important for the
OL,11,Fgovernment to recognise why we've done
OL,12,Fso badly in it."
OL,14,FHe added that he is "not calling for a
OL,15,Fchange of leadership" but does want a
OL,16,F"change in the direction of travel
OL,17,Fwith this government."
OL,19,FThe mayor also spoke of the difficulty
OL,20,Fof campaigning in London. He said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,F"I keep hearing anger, disillusionment
OL,8,Fand disappointment.
OL,10,F"And the direction of that anger,
OL,11,Fdissolution and disappointment is the
OL,12,FLabour government. The promises made
OL,13,Fin July 2024 haven't been delivered.
OL,15,F"There needs to be change and there
OL,16,Fneeds to be an acceleration in terms
OL,17,Fof delivery and where there has been
OL,18,Fsome real achievements from the Labour
OL,19,Fgovernment, they've been overshadowed
OL,20,Fby mistakes and mishaps over the last
OL,21,Fsix weeks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778418667
OL,3,C"Anger, disillusionment and
OL,4,Cdisappointment" : Sir Sadiq Khan on
OL,5,CLabour's losses
OL,7,F"We've been talking about Peter
OL,8,FMandelson for the last six weeks when
OL,9,Fwe could have been talking about some
OL,10,Fof the achievements of the Labour
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"I'm angry. I'm really angry. And I'm
OL,14,Fheartbroken for those excellent
OL,15,Fcouncillors who've lost their seats
OL,16,Ffor some excellent Labour councils
OL,17,Fthat are no longer Labour councils.
OL,19,F"These are great public servants who
OL,20,Fhave lost their seats through a fault
OL,21,Fof their own. That makes me angry."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
